			<h2>Reservation Cards</h2>
			<p>Reservation cards can be created via two different markups. <em>Standard markup</em> is supported via <code>theme-mylt/_card.scss</code>, and represents the way these cards function within the reservation tool. <em>Notecard markup</em> is intended to demonstrate the framework tools built into <code>theme-base/_card-notecard.scss</code> and the addition of color classes via <code>theme-base/_card-suits.scss</code> if you wish to recreate the look of these cards for other use cases.</p>
			<p>Please note that margins have switched to be entirely margin-bottom based for consistency in the <em>Notecard</em> version. I've used margin-bottom on the headings to equalize this difference in these examples.</p>

			<h5 class="m-t-3">Closed/Unavailable/Reservation</h5>
